## Common Troubleshooting

### Build Errors Documented

- [x] **cargo: command not found** — Rust installation and PATH setup
- [x] **Polars compilation errors** — Version compatibility (use v0.32.1)
- [x] **Borrowing/ownership errors** — Clone data structures
- [x] **Feature not found** — Feature flags in Cargo.toml

### Runtime Errors Documented

- [x] **No such file or directory** (loan-recovery.csv) — Running from wrong directory
- [x] **Permission denied** — File system permissions
- [x] **Polars-specific errors** (SchemaMismatch) — Column names and data types

### Performance Issues Documented

- [x] **Slow compilation** — First build is normal (~1-2 min)
- [x] **Out of memory** — Close other apps, use release mode
- [x] **Large file processing** — Memory limitations noted, streaming API planned

### Debugging Steps

- [x] Verify Rust installation: `rustc --version`
- [x] Check file permissions: `ls -la`
- [x] Clean build: `cargo clean && cargo build`
- [x] Check dependencies: `cargo tree`

